dct_title_s: Davis Strait, Greenland (Denmark)--west coast, Aqissersiorfik (Rypeo) to Nuuk (Godthab) (Raster Image)
dct_description_sm: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From a Danish chart of 1971." Not distributed to depository libraries. Place names in Greenlandic and Danish with glossary in English. "Copyright 1998 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes tidal information. Map no.38546.
This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
